{"word":"ὀλέκω","slug":"ὀλέκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n72934\" key=\"o)le/kw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀλέκω</orth>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> without augm. <sense id=\"n72934.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄλεκον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:150\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.150</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; Iterat. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀλέκεσκον</foreign> (<xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.l.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ὀλέεσκον</ref> </xr>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:135\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.135</biblScope> </bibl> :—<tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀλέσκω</orth> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl> :—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ruin, destroy, kill,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> always in last sense, and mostly of men, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἱ δ᾽ ἀλλήλους ὀλέκουσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:172\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.172</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.249</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:108\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.108</biblScope></bibl>, etc. ; but in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:305\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.305</biblScope></bibl>, of birds which <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">prey</tr_> on smaller birds, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἱ δέ τε τὰς ὀλέκουσιν ἐπάλμενοι</foreign> : in Philos., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τίκτει τ᾽ ὀλέκει τε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1342.tlg001:17:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Emp.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.4</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> :—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">perish, die,</tr_> esp. a violent death, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀλέκοντο δὲ λαοί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.10</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.17</biblScope></bibl>.—Chiefly <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram></gramGrp>, used by Trag. only in lyr., once in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τί μ᾽ ὀλέκεις</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1285\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1285</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); twice in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀλέκει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:563\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">563</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>(anap.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὠλεκόμαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1012\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1012</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (lyr.): later, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg032:10:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ LXX\">LXX</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Jb.\">Jb.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.16</biblScope> </bibl> :—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg032